(1) Breakpoints
-----------------
==> Breakpoints are the triggers in Bootstrap for how your layout responsive changes across device or viewport sizes.


(2) Available breakpoints
---------------------------
==> x-small : 0â€“576px [Not Have Class In Bootstrap5]
==> sm      : >= 576px
==> md      : >= 768px
==> lg      : >= 992px
==> xl      : >= 1200px
==> xxl     : >= 1400px
